# Changes

## 0.5.0

- adds `entry` endpoint to facade making it a DTS level 1 server
- adds `@context` to entry response object

## 0.4.0

- adds `provider` and `location` path parameters for every facade
  endpoint that allow to select a resource provider (by values of
  `file`, `urn` or `doi`) and a remote base location accessed through
  the provider. Thus collection gets
  `/{provider}/{location}/collection{id}{?nav}`. Other endpoints
  similar.
- adds tags to endpoints
- removes the `direct` parameter again

## 0.3.1

- adds extra endpoint for default collection

## 0.3.0

- makes `id` of the collection endpoint and `resource` of navigation
  and document a path parameter in the facade for better IRI
  management
- makes both paramters URIs for better encoding of complex URL-like
  identifiers
- adds `direct` flag parameter to the facade for controling internal
  access to resources on SEED XC

## 0.2.0

- adds collection endpoint to the facade

## 0.1.1

- make `cf` and `cf` objects map to `Map<String, String>` hash map

## 0.1.0

- introduces deep objects `cf` and `cr` to the DTS facade for passing around resources and followup information.

## 0.0.3

- adds free-form @context property to `Navigation` object
- adds @type property to `CiteStructure` object

## 0.0.1

- follows the 1.0rc1 specs of DTS

## 0.0.1-rc10

- follows the 1.0rc1 specs of DTS
- entry endpoint
- collection endpoint
